HEADWORD: Untruthful
<hw>Un*truth"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not truthful;
unveracious; contrary to the truth or the fact.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Un*truth"ful*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Un*truth"ful*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
